------------------------------------------------------------


DESCRIPTION
-----------
tfshow is a simple tool to traffic analyze or *tcp kill* (send
tcp rst). I'm using with toolkit into fwguardian project.


RUNNING (LINUX)
---------------
You configure it via command line parameters.

Example:
tfshow -i eth0


PARAMETERS
----------------
command line       Description
------------------------------------------------------------
-i                 Sniffed interface
-p                 Disable promisc mode
-f                 Define a pcap filter
-r                 Number of rows in display 
-k                 Work in *tcp Kill* mode
